text: Jean-Claude Cloët (born 11 July 1951) is a retired French football defender and later manager.Weltfussball He was a part of the France B team that finished runners-up at the 1975 Mediterranean Games. ==References== Category:1951 births Category:Living people Category:French footballers Category:Valenciennes FC players Category:AS Nancy players Category:AS Cannes players Category:CO Saint-Dizier players Category:Association football defenders Category:Ligue 1 players Category:French football managers Category:Stade de Reims managers Category:Competitors at the 1975 Mediterranean Games Category:Mediterranean Games competitors for France
